{"tid":2039889,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Steam 中國版曝光  將滿足中國政府要求","createTime":"2020-05-28T08:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T09:25:27.000Z","uid":123991,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ede191d5b5fb152ebd211c97c2fd110141bb5129","tid":2039889,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T08:56:18.000Z","msg":"柒到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/41efb170-4cc4-11ea-bffb-6cd8ed80fa4d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F41efb170-4cc4-11ea-bffb-6cd8ed80fa4d.jpeg&h=cb7a59ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n儘管 Valve 在 2018 年宣布會推出 Steam 中國版，但一直都未有更多消息，直至最近，終於有指 Steam 中國版的  Alpha 版本將在本周釋出。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據 Steam 客戶端的最新更新顯示，Valve 仍在開發 Steam 中國版，且已正式進入 Alpha 階段。雖然目前仍未正式推出官方伺服器，但該客戶端已經包含了中國官方「批准」的認證標誌。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nSteam 中國版以 Steam 原版為基樣，作出了三項針對中國用戶的改動，分別為「新增節制遊戲提醒」、「過濾處理個人資料」，以及「限制遊戲時間」。在開啟遊戲時，玩家會看見類似 DPRC 的強制性訊息，該訊息會鼓勵中國公民保持節制，顯示「過度遊戲對身體有害」等的警告字句，而該彈出信息將會停留在畫面上 5 秒。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Foriginal.jpg&h=230c5106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，所有的個人資資訊都將被 Steam 進行了過濾處，所有的個人資料圖片都會使用默認的 Steam 問號圖片取代，其餘個人資料亦會被轉換為 Steam 專有的 Steam ID 編號。即中國版 Steam 並不允許玩家自定義個人資料圖片以及 ID 名稱，且有可能需要先通過中國政府的審批才可成功註冊。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/original-1-594x580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Foriginal-1-594x580.jpg&h=67ea61bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，Valve 似乎也在限制玩家在特定時間段內不能玩遊戲，此舉似乎與中國政府去年 11月 制定的指導方針一脈相承。中國對於未成年人士玩網上遊戲有相當大的限制。外媒《<a href=\"http://win.gg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwin.gg&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5Ps0BU04RHr%2BP31d0xuhNw0M%3D&h=55e35e1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">win.gg</a>》試過在中國清晨五點的時間開啟《CS：GO》，但中國版 Steam 跳出警告訊息並阻止啟動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/original-2-768x332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Foriginal-2-768x332.jpg&h=405860b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然似乎有不少的限制，但至少 Steam 中國版是真有其事，且 Valve 亦相當樂意配合中國當局的要求。"},{"pid":"615c3ef3eb922de271bc922ecd03e4379242fece","tid":2039889,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"笑乜嘢 德政嚟"},{"pid":"c91b3c5b60f1cf753d77908e3a221e50983fa9f3","tid":2039889,"uid":189528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"集中營，冇名得編號"},{"pid":"6c693e3cfebafd187f557839657d62bbde066cb5","tid":2039889,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5c1deb26366cd49f296d3f5662dd6c1a0a9865","tid":2039889,"uid":103374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"玩貪食蛇呀？"},{"pid":"f8590a93f57d9296ca1966af3288cefa9e65b7fb","tid":2039889,"uid":38784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"笑乜鳩呀 國安法都立埋 遲早到我地"},{"pid":"ff0e961d6e47d50b94b4856b7bafc28c69291d53","tid":2039889,"uid":123848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:09:39.000Z","msg":"外國玩家真喺會多謝你肯封國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立即小咗99%外掛"},{"pid":"c61a2382dfcf20e1ce5c2d8983925f79a89594dd","tid":2039889,"uid":103363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:14:15.000Z","msg":"唔好笑住呀<br />\n香港跟住架喇<br />\n不過我作為steam 嘅用家能夠同支共攬炒予有榮焉"},{"pid":"0a0971d488e48abf9cdb6b